Start function main 
  * Prompt user to enter customer ID number
  * Prompt user to enter package letter
  * Prompt user to enter total hours used
  * Call function calcBill
  * Call function dispOutput
  * Return
End Function main

Start function calcBill
  * Calculate cost of bill
  * Return bill
End function calcBill

Start function dispOutput
  * Display header
  * Display customer number
  * Display package purchased
  * Display hours used
  * Display total monthly bill
  * Return
End function dispOutput
